{
  "id": "adv_main_01_02_05",
  "title": "星見編1章11話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（月に照らされて、琴乃はダンスを続けている）\n（その姿はまるで一つの芸術作品のようだった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kotono continues to dance in the moonlight.）\n（She looks like a work of art.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（そこから放たれるオーラは、圧倒的だ）\n（紛れもなく麻奈の妹だった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Her aura she gives off is hypnotic‚ impactful.）\n（She is unquestionably Mana’s younger sister.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.433333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage1",
      "startTime": 16.58712011973063
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "――誰？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who’s there?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.787120119730638,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.08712011973063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あまりに美しかったから、つい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ I was mesmerized by your dancing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.62045345306397,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃はどう答えていいか分からないようだ）\n（そこに月が差す。琴乃は月明かりを見上げる）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Kotono appears unsure of how to reply.）\n（Then a moonbeam shines down on her‚ and she looks up.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "……月、綺麗ですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The moon… It’s beautiful.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2537867863973,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "私、月が好きなんです。小さかった頃\n家族みんなで海に遊びに行ったことがあって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love the moon. When I was little‚\nmy family and I took a trip to the beach‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.82235699171821,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ちょうど台風で全然海にも入れなくて\n太陽すら見ることができなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but there was a hurricane‚ so we couldn’t swim in the ocean.\nThe sun wasn’t even out.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.140171985700725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "でも、夜になったら満月が見えたんです\n――それを見て思った",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But at night‚ there was a beautiful full moon.\nAnd when I saw it‚ a thought hit me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.77878214144239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn007.m4a",
      "text": "月って何も照らしてないように見えて\n真っ暗な夜を照らしているんだなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The moon may not seem bright‚\nbut it’s actually our light in the darkness of night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 62.274917960897376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn008.m4a",
      "text": "太陽みたいに生命の源にはなれないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So while it may not be the source of life like the sun is‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.27878214144239,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn009.m4a",
      "text": "誰かをひっそりと\n人知れず元気づけているんだなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "the moon still brings people joy and courage‚\nout of sight…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.85903955994577,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn010.m4a",
      "text": "そういうの、いいなって\n――もちろん、アイドルが人知れず、じゃダメですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And I just think that’s lovely.\nOf course‚ idols shouldn’t be out of sight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.68564243431724,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn011.m4a",
      "text": "……{user}さんは\nどう思います？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nWhat do you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.25230910098391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn012.m4a",
      "text": "さくらの歌声……\nお姉ちゃんに似てると思いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "About Sakura’s voice…\nDo you think it sounds like my sister’s?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.08564243431725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "………………気になるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Has that been on your mind?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.75230910098391,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn013.m4a",
      "text": "……私、お姉ちゃんの歌声を\n小さい頃から聞いてきたから分かるんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve…listened to my sister sing since I was a kid.\nSo I know.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.66073231923919,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn014.m4a",
      "text": "自分にはないものだって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That I can't have that voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.91897576765056,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn015.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスも、音階や発声だって、頑張ればうまくなれる\nでも、あの声は出せない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can get better at dancing and even singing with practice.\nBut I’ll never be able to sing like her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.05230910098396,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn016.m4a",
      "text": "あんなに心が柔らかくなるような声\n私には出せない……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My voice will never be that soothing.\nI can’t sing like that….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.94036796005838,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "声は人それぞれだからね\n琴乃には琴乃の声があっていいと思うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ everybody has their unique voice.\nI think your voice is special in its own way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn017.m4a",
      "text": "今まではそう思ってました\nでもさくらは出せるんです、あの声が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’ve told myself that all these years.\nBut Sakura has that magic voice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.15167425361544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn018.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの素晴らしい歌声が",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The beautiful‚ magical voice my sister had.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.95167425361544,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "……それで、悩んでいたのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Is that what’s been bothering you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4850075869488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "――センターは、さくらにして下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’d like you to make Sakura our center.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.2850075869488,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "その方がきっと\nお姉ちゃんの目指したステージに近くなる……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know that if you do that‚\nit’ll take us closer to the stage my sister dreamed of reaching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 141.20605068094798,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 145.97271734761472
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 145.97271734761472
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_outside-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 146.206050680948
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-mna001.m4a",
      "text": "迷ってるんでしょ\n琴乃とさくら、どっちをセンターにするか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re conflicted‚ aren’t you?\nYou can’t choose between Kotono and Sakura.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.90705927001707,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mna",
      "speakerName": "長瀬麻奈",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05/sud_vo_adv_main_01_02_05-mna002.m4a",
      "text": "いっそ\n二人でセンターで歌わせたらいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚\nwhy don’t you just have them share the center?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.6393840142814,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshiarcade-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "stage2",
      "startTime": 155.90664590683855
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
